Author: axanax_lattepls
Text: Tbh same, I mean I've always had odd eating habits but I was with my best friend at this specialty cafe and it look me like 10-15 minutes to order a coffee, when they had every vegan milk under the sun so realistically it shouldn't have been that difficult but the lack of calories on the menu had me nervous because every barista is different, and what if someone uses too much oat milk, or adds sweetener or worse cane sugar without me knowing? Hyper-awareness sucks sometimes.
